</guid></item><item><title>战时考验以色列的民主</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/testing-israels-democracy-in-wartime/0000018b-495e-d5d2-afef-cdffc47a0000</guid></item><item><title>睁大眼睛：以色列情报部门对哈马斯的军事集结视而不见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:18:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/eyes-wide-shut-israeli-intelligence-was-blind-to-hamas-military-build-up/0000018b-4906-d03a-afcb-693e52210000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对抗更强大的以色列的长期目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 21:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-long-term-goals-in-its-fight-against-a-stronger-israel/0000018b-493f-d5d2-afef-cdff422d0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯真的像伊斯兰国吗？专家讲解</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</link><description>是否有可能与哈马斯合作？十二位研究伊斯兰团体及其历史的学者努力确定它是如何成为今天的怪物的，并提出了行动方案</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:57:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-hamas-really-like-isis-experts-explain/0000018b-493f-d1fd-a59f-edbfbe090000</guid></item><item><title>武装警卫保护本周末在美国校园参加安息日活动的犹太学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</link><description>希勒尔国际总裁表示，我们需要对真正的威胁保持警惕。在针对加沙战争的一波反以色列集会之后，犹太学生组织正在向大学施压，要求其加强安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 20:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/armed-guards-to-protect-jewish-students-attending-shabbat-events-on-u-s-campuses/0000018b-4996-d1fd-a59f-ed9f70eb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯袭击后失踪的一些人将无法找到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</link><description>根据以色列国防军的最新数据，有 100 至 200 人被列为失踪人员，随着以色列继续寻找尸体，这一数字预计会发生变化。据军方了解，约有 30 名 16 岁以下儿童被绑架</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:57:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-believes-some-of-those-missing-after-hamas-attack-will-not-be-found/0000018b-4942-d5d2-afef-cdff5b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正式加入美国免签证计划，立即生效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</link><description>以色列入境原定于 11 月 30 日开始，但由于哈马斯袭击后美国驻以色列大使馆暂停签证处理，迫于国会压力，这一进程已加快。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 19:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-officially-in-the-u-s-visa-waiver-program-effective-immediately/0000018b-4972-d5d2-afef-cdffdb9a0000</guid></item><item><title>2007年的内塔尼亚胡：总理对国家安全负有个人责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</link><description>“在像以色列这样的国家，如果一个人不具备某种塑造外交安全概念的能力，你就不能任命他为总理，因为如果是这样，那么这些机构就真正具有统治力；内塔尼亚胡向一个正在调查 2006 年第二次黎巴嫩战争的委员会作证说：“他不控制这些机构，也不指导它们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 18:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-in-2007-the-prime-minister-bears-personal-responsibility-for-national-security/0000018b-491b-d1fd-a59f-ed9b113e0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人没有安全的地方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</link><description>以色列最伟大的成就之一是它为本国公民以及世界各地的犹太人提供的安全和繁荣，让他们偶尔忘记自己面临着犹太人的仇恨。从以色列南部到澳大利亚悉尼，情况已不再如此</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 17:23:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/there-is-no-safe-place-for-the-jews/0000018b-487b-d03a-afcb-697b23400000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在安曼举行的中东峰会可能已取消，但美国仍应采取严肃的外交行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</link><description>拜登等美国总统周三的访问可能会成为中东外交的一个重大转折点，但问题是这是否是白宫想要的</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:44:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/bidens-summit-in-amman-may-have-been-cancelled-but-the-u-s-should-still-pursue-diplomacy/0000018b-489b-d1fd-a59f-ed9bf1a10000</guid></item><item><title>“我没有时间哀悼母亲被杀，因为我必须拯救孩子们的生命”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</link><description>被哈马斯绑架进入加沙地带的儿童家属召开新闻发布会，恳求内塔尼亚胡、以色列政府和国际社会帮助释放人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 16:41:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-dont-have-time-to-mourn-my-mothers-murder-because-i-have-to-save-my-childrens-life/0000018b-488d-d03a-afcb-69bf4ff60000</guid></item><item><title>共和党人将呼吁加沙停火的犹太抗议者与 1 月 6 日的叛乱分子进行了比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</link><description>众议员马乔里·泰勒·格林（Marjorie Taylor Greene）是支持特朗普的支持者之一，呼吁将周三在国会办公室静坐的数百名美国犹太抗议者“关押在华盛顿特区的古拉格集中营”，将他们的行为等同于所给予的治疗致 2021 年袭击国会大厦的人们</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 15:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/gop-compares-jewish-protesters-calling-for-gaza-cease-fire-to-january-6-insurrectionists/0000018b-481d-d242-abef-5a3f310d0000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德囚犯交换专家警告说，“释放以色列人质的机会之窗正在关闭”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/window-of-opportunity-to-free-israeli-hostages-is-closing-we-have-a-week/0000018b-482f-d5d2-afef-ccff4a650000</link><description>沙利特囚犯交换背后的摩萨德资深人士大卫·梅丹认为，哈马斯有兴趣迅速达成协议，释放被俘的以色列儿童、妇女和老人。他警告说，如果我们等到战后，许多人质将不再活着。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 15:50:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/window-of-opportunity-to-free-israeli-hostages-is-closing-we-have-a-week/0000018b-482f-d5d2-afef-ccff4a650000</guid></item><item><title>NSO 和以色列网络公司帮助追踪失踪的以色列人和人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cyber-arms-and-intelligence-firms-like-nso-aiding-israeli-efforts/0000018b-4813-de3d-a58f-c87b7d950000</link><description>从面部识别到开源情报和进攻性网络，NSO、Rayzone 等公司以及 AnyVision 等公司帮助绘制和跟踪人质和伤亡人员的情况</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cyber-arms-and-intelligence-firms-like-nso-aiding-israeli-efforts/0000018b-4813-de3d-a58f-c87b7d950000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯大使将加沙暴力归咎于西方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/russian-ambassador-blames-west-for-gaza-violence/0000018b-4838-d5d2-afef-ccfd4f2c0000</link><description>俄罗斯驻以色列特使阿纳托利·维克托罗夫在俄罗斯官方媒体 RT 频道上谴责西方：“他们并不是真的想帮助制止暴力”</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/russian-ambassador-blames-west-for-gaza-violence/0000018b-4838-d5d2-afef-ccfd4f2c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会道德委员会因将加沙战争与大屠杀联系起来而暂停并扣留 MK 的薪酬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-ethics-committee-suspends-docks-pay-of-mk-for-tying-gaza-war-to-holocaust/0000018b-4815-d614-abcf-e87795490000</link><description>奥弗·卡西夫 (MK Ofer Cassif) 在接受有关以色列与哈马斯战争的采访时将右翼财政部长斯莫特里奇提出的计划称为“最终解决方案”，因此将被扣掉 14 天的工资。卡西夫表示，这一决定是政治言论自由棺材上的一颗钉子</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 14:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-19/ty-article/.premium/knesset-ethics-committee-suspends-docks-pay-of-mk-for-tying-gaza-war-to-holocaust/0000018b-4815-d614-abcf-e87795490000</guid></item><item><title>葡萄牙采取行动终止塞法迪犹太公民身份法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/portugal-moves-to-end-sephardi-jewish-citizenship-law/0000018b-4818-d614-abcf-e87ba3530000</link><description>继西班牙之后，葡萄牙政界人士旨在废除允许伊比利亚血统的犹太人获得公民身份的法律；到 2022 年底，约 75,000 人获得公民身份</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Oct 2023 13:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-10-19/ty-article/portugal-moves-to-end-sephardi-jewish-citizenship-law/0000018b-4818-d614-abcf-e87ba3530000</guid></item></channel></rss>